div2.p:
Those elements in the above list which are not defined elsewhere have
the following formal declarations:

&titlePage;
&docTitle;
&titlePart;
&docAuthor;
&imprimatur;
&docEdition;
&docImprint;
&docDate;

The back element; since there are no other specialized
back-matter tags, nothing else is defined here.

&back;
